{"tid":1568741,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港似乎已患上了「白血球過多症」","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T12:05:42.000Z","uid":149978,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"333dba18570e1b3367f4901845233a63627f9968","tid":1568741,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"如果香港係一個大身體，警察係白血球<br />\n香港已經患上了白血球過多症<br />\n非常危險<br />\n================<br />\n「白血球過多症」，源於負責製造血液的骨髓生產過多的不成熟白血球引起，雖然數量很大，但不能像正常白細胞抵抗感染，還直接影響正常健康血細胞的產量，導致紅血球、白血球與血小板的數量低下，身體免疫系統降低、器官運作緩慢，若不及時醫治，急性白血球過多症可致命。"},{"pid":"4c8abf74d41e83571a35db5097b796f938cc9fe0","tid":1568741,"uid":54126,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:17:15.000Z","msg":"癌症啊"},{"pid":"0386079087acac5c866d33c70bcd4651c2c3efe1","tid":1568741,"uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"正常黎講，popo貴精不貴多<br />\n<br />\n香港太多劣質popo"},{"pid":"268030b5598087343089c66b1548be0f9ccf318c","tid":1568741,"uid":255489,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:22:28.000Z","msg":"即係白血病?!好難醫架喎!"},{"pid":"d855931f859281bc35b6a4683a5555fdc75d343d","tid":1568741,"uid":104684,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"血癌"},{"pid":"d3fbceef7e228cd21a27ce09b71703c7b9d15e85","tid":1568741,"uid":17402,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0386079087acac5c866d33c70bcd4651c2c3efe1","tid":1568741,"uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"正常黎講，popo貴精不貴多<br />\n<br />\n香港太多劣質popo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"讀書唔成做警察<br />\n竟然要拎班讀書唔成既人管住其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959a9f0755931308f222abd39e1a15d3118c39a4","tid":1568741,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"268030b5598087343089c66b1548be0f9ccf318c","tid":1568741,"uid":255489,"like":3,"d